{
  "stem": "21437.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he sort of was willing it to happen, that we will leave Olkusz, that we won't be separated.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it took me a long time to acknowledge that it was, even-- even him, who I refused to believe that he couldn't handle a situation.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But that even him, who meant everything to me, who always kept his promises-- my parents always-- they didn't say anything that they couldn't promise.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So and then he didn't keep his-- he didn't keep his promise.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was this part which is still in me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This part-- the longing is there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is something that you-- I accept it, and I acknowledge it, that I might have grown.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Growth, personal growth was very important to me later on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I know you have to work on it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's hard work.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You have to face yourself and face your surroundings.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But this part, I allow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This child within me, this part where it was the separation, where it was a very difficult-- this, I realized right there and then.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I didn't want to.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Not-- I didn't-- everything locked-- locked in me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I couldn't swallow anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I couldn't-- I didn't know anybody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I didn't-- I didn't want to.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I-- I'm not saying that I was-- I don't think so my spirit was broken, just my physical.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The physical self couldn't cope with it anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "As we will see later on, apparently the spiritual part, you know, apparently came to the fore.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Because a few days later, I don't know how it happened, because there was nothing there to read.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
